descriptionHtml:
I have Made Alexstrasza In RaceMenu And Uploaded It To Nexus For All Of You Guys To Enjoy.P.S I Am A Big Fan Of MXR.

INSTALLATION: Download Manually drag and drop all content into where ever your chargen folder is located. then put Alexstrasza V1.jslot into preset folder inside the chargen folder.
REQUIRED MODS: Fair Skin Complexionhttp://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D51602%26preview%3D&pUp=1

COVEREYES:http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/4869/?

APACHIISKYHAIR:http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?



 Download only "ALEXSTRASZA V1 racemenu preset"
Extract the Alexstrasza V1.nif Alexstrasza V1.jslot and Alexstrasza V1.dds into data/skse/plugins/chargen folder then copy Alexstrasza V1.jslot into data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets 
Go into showracemenu,
Select the one called "Alexstrasza V1.jslot" and hit enter.
Alexstrasza appears !
